# =============================================================================
# FORGE MISSION CONTROL — Orion (Chief of Staff) config TEMPLATE (.env.example)
#
# Copy to  mission.env  (git-ignored, lives OUTSIDE the web root, 404s over HTTP).
# Orion reuses whatever Anthropic key is already wired for the other businesses, so
# NOTHING here is required — this file only exists if you want a DEDICATED key or to
# tune the daily cadence. Orion is read-only + propose: he synthesizes the owner's
# "attack today" brief; he never takes an outward action.
# =============================================================================

# --- Orion's OWN Claude key (optional) ---------------------------------------
# If unset, Orion falls back to the agency → dropship → wholesale key resolver, so
# the cross-business brief works as soon as ANY business has a key.
# MISSION_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Cadence knobs -----------------------------------------------------------
# Local hour (FORGE_TZ_OFFSET zone) after which the box builds today's CEO brief,
# once per day. Opening the dashboard reads the CACHED brief (instant + free); a paid
# Claude call only runs on this daily build or when you tap Refresh.
# FORGE_MISSION_BRIEF_HOUR=7
# Briefs before Orion auto-improves his playbook (manual "Learn" button ignores this).
# FORGE_MISSION_LEARN_EVERY=10
# Push the CEO brief to Telegram each morning (1 = on). Off by default — the dashboard
# greeting is the primary surface.
# FORGE_MISSION_BRIEF_TELEGRAM=0
